Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:04.78,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}数十億もの 鼓動の数さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:11.63,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}貴方には瞬き程度の些事な等級
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:16.62,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}過去に因われて未来を嘆くも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:22.50,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}塵一つ誤算を許さぬ必然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:28.85,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}無限に広がる夢も 描く未来も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:34.46,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}僕たちに許された虚栄の権利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:40.61,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}有限 それは二つの針が示す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:45.50,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}残酷な約定と選択へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:47.66,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}Hacking to the Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:54.64,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}だから今 一秒ごとに世界線を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:59.74,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}君のその笑顔 守りたいのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:06.61,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}そしてまた 悲しみのない時間のループへと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:12.92,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}飲み込まれていく 孤独の観測者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:04.78,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}就连数十亿生物的鼓动之数
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:11.63,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(100,100)}也不过如对你眨眼般琐碎的等级
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:16.62,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}即使叹息囚禁于过去的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:22.50,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}也无法容许微小误算的必然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:28.85,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}无限扩展的梦想 描绘而出的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:34.46,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(100,100)}都是我们被允许的虚荣权利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:40.61,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}有限 此为两支时针所昭示的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:45.50,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}指向残酷的约定与选择
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:47.66,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}Hacking to the Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:54.64,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}所以此刻 只凭一秒即可穿越世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:59.74,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}想要守护你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:06.61,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}然后再次 去往没有悲伤的时间轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:12.92,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}逐渐吞噬消失 孤独的观测者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然说我是救世主?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是疯狂的科学狂人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望是破坏与混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏掉了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:44.31,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,658)}Operation Urd
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 「掌管过去的女神」行动再次展开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可显像管氏还在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.22,0:00:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我应该说过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反对什么? 白天不是说会支持的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说…果然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 实验已经进行过了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去已经因为D-MAIL而改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说世界线已经改变了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你们失去了改变前的一部分记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个什么六合彩吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 为什么只有你一个人还保留着记忆啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.47,0:01:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提托说过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.72,0:01:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拥有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了确认这点必须得让世界线再次进行移动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.68,0:01:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.34,0:01:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使跨越世界线 也依然保留记忆的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔眼 Reading Steiner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:20.97,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(779,652)}梦幻的动态平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桶子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有发送记录 收件的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 D-MAIL发到五天前了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去改变了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你怎么还记得这事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向五天前的桶子发送D-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉了他菲利斯杯的卡片情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桶子应该赢了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真由氏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事想问你下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的菲利斯杯 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶? 输了吗? 被秒杀?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~这样啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 那就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给桶子的邮件并没有改变过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏的走向应该确实被改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度不足以改变世界线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定得是能让我们轻易观察到过去是否改变的邮件…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有赞成实验的意思!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于只有你一个人能保留记忆这点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是魔眼Reading Steiner的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是为了确认这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次该你来发送D-MAIL了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心时间悖论吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变过去…总觉得很卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我的人生只有18年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不想改变它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包含失败在内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是自己的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…却最爱做实验 没错吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢有错嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说自己作壁上观
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边欣赏别人的牺牲 一边偷笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是科学狂人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 说正经的…
