Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 冈伦也有份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃小姐早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我说 后来怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间机器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问过约翰·提托了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过我开始搞不懂那家伙说的是否正确了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一块啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这么激动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你是个提托宅?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 克里斯酱 嘟嘟噜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good Morning
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 又擦出火花了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架很让人难过的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止私人性质的邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好是那种能简单判断出过去是否改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四天之前我换了手机的机型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但想告诉自己还是不换比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果过去改变了 桐生小姐的手机也会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一目了然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 实验开始!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 电话烤箱（暂定） 启动…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好圆呐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈…凶真先生托我买的六合彩 我搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是赔礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗 那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…心意很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离你睁开心眼的日子也不远了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那么我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就走了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好像也挺忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次会来穿真由喜的Cos吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我对这些东西还是有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得会很合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是…这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去…改变了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:24.05,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(576,660)}Shining Finger
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪光的指压师在哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shi…哈?
