Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用日语就OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉华子他…没来过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉华君? 没来过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那萌郁呢 萌郁怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌郁? 那是谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐生萌郁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她今天没来吗 到底来没来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐生萌郁? 我也没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你又用D-MAIL了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 等…这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去发生了改变 使萌郁整个人都消失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收信记录里直到7月31号前 萌郁的邮件记录都还留着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz6\fs50\bord0\be1\pos(757,286)}我是萌郁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在有点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会再给你发短信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 在四天前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到了邮件的桐生…萌郁小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的行动发生了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致过去变成了她没有来Lab的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 这次也只有你一人记得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…Reading Steiner来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带一提 你这个造词太丢人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得还是不要用了比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的个人见解是不必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越世界线也能保留记忆的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事明天再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦 明天见～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份力量是真实的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.81,0:12:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:40.11,Default_tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字：希望你能成为救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那些人居然能在Lab过夜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说这样才算是科学狂人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 下次大家一起来过夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要男生就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:13:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 要不要来我住的酒店?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那下次我就去打扰你喽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉华君 嘟嘟噜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 真的?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然没带妖刀五月雨?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦 冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉华君今天可是真由喜的客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是来穿真由喜的COS服的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来来 琉华君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来变身吧 变身变身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 脱掉脱掉衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不要碰那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道了 我自己穿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 不要碰那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿这个可是有诀窍的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 别脱了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常…百合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.14,0:14:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 琉华子是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更没羞没臊了
