Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…让我有成为超低视角摄影者的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦你觉得怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在正遭受着强烈的精神冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 内心…内心要被侵蚀了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了 凶真先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 又在闹什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯酱 嘟嘟噜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变态助手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么从头到脚打量人家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了 没羞没臊的展开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 这个COS服 适合琉华君吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很cute哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,c…cute…哪有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也试穿下别的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有事想求你们帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是来穿COS服的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我说过不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都不听我说话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉哦 太开心了不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你有什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想发送邮件到过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天…本来想送弄错六合彩的赔礼来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说又用D-MAIL了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 等…这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去发生了改变 使萌郁整个人都消失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不想偷听你们说话的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉华君 你想给过去发送怎样的邮件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想变成女生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不大喜欢自己的相貌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能变成女生的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定能多些自信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前就这么想了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到底在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 助手 看来你犯了一个决定性的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错误?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉华子不是女生 是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是肤浅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是科学家的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用自己的双眼好好确认一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么可爱的孩子怎么可能会是男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 冒犯一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是认真的 我真的想变成女生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 仅靠发送D-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未必真的能改变性别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听过一个传言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在怀孕期间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃肉的话 会生男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃蔬菜的话 就会生女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想发送D-MAIL 告诉你母亲要多吃蔬菜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 不行吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我来实现你的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 琉华君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变性别是不是太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为这事靠吃点蔬菜就能办成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是有科学依据的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是他烦恼的事而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样能让他满意的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉华子 从今天开始你就是我们Lab的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Labmem No.006
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就赶快进行实验吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今年是17岁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说是1993出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机开始在日本普及是什么时候的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是1996年左右的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有邮件功能时似乎还要更晚一些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 在漆原出生的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他母亲很有可能没有手机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就发不了D-MAIL了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:19:00.28,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300, 300)}毒电波
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:19:00.49,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:19:00.28,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300, 300)}每当拥有严重妄想癖的人主张自己要接收电波、或者是要发送电波的时候，\N这种被“发送”/“接收”的电波就叫做毒电波。有时也会用来称呼这些发送/接收毒电波的人。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改造成能发射毒电波如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒电波有你们就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真好 再多骂我一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的才能真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又想说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有手机的话 发送到BP机不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BP机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过电波 向小型接收器发送信号的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于1990年代爆发般普及起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后因为手机的普及而销声匿迹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BP机?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个东西我第一次见识到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:37.48,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300, 300)}Saleser
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:37.65,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:37.48,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300, 300)}销售经理。\N与celeb发音相似。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真清楚啊 不是土十七而是推销员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那写着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己读
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Labmem No.006 漆原琉华
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First Mission
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查你母亲是否有BP机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后弄到号码
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈有BP机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是号码
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑好邮件的内容了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃一些蔬菜的话就能生下健康的孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我听说只能发送18个平假名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BP机只能发送数字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个变换成数字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像浊音符号必须得用两个数字来表示啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能发送的只有半角36个文字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话就超出了四个字符
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:33.75,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300, 300)}此处变更
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:33.91,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:33.75,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300, 300)}食べる→食う。\N意义没有变化。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个变换成数字的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-5\fs30\bord0\be2\1c&H706D62&\pos(434,445)}多食蔬菜的话就能生下健康的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了吗 那就启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reading Steiner发动了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 也有这种人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这个很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这个绝对很适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 变态
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你盯着哪里看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「琉华子是不是变成女孩子了」这种话很难问出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个平度…是失败了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我·说·你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一脸傻笑 到底在构思什么样的变态行为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头痛啊 真是不能对你们这对变态组合掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是变态啦 是变态绅士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样都好 真的是怎样都好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:02.46,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 桶子君不是变态是绅士哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 世界线确实移动了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:03.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被他毒害了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…是什么…



Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:10.97,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------- ED first non-black frame -------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.18,0:22:28.78,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規制された視界 無慈悲なる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.15,0:22:37.54,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二の支配 逃れられない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:45.96,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安息の明日を願った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.71,0:22:55.10,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手の中の尊い事象の地平へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.30,0:23:03.90,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囚われし盟約 現れた偽証の輪郭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.06,0:23:13.03,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命の天地は盲目な時間を刻んで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:18.04,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽ばたけバタフライ 奇跡のバタフライ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:21.92,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたへ捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:26.30,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙のバタフライ 眩しいバタフライ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:33.81,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全てが 今書き換えられる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.18,0:22:28.78,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被限制的视界 毫无慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.15,0:22:37.54,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二条的支配 无从逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:45.96,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾祈求安息的明日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.71,0:22:55.10,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去向手中珍贵现象的地平线
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.30,0:23:03.90,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被囚禁的盟约 出现的伪证轮廓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.06,0:23:13.03,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命的天地即铭刻于盲目的时间之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:18.04,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飞吧蝴蝶 奇迹的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:21.92,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向你奉献一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:26.30,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪水闪耀的蝴蝶 炫目的蝴蝶
